   <div  class='  py-8 md:py-8 px-4 md:px-16'>
      <div class="container mx-auto p-10 max-w-[900px]">

      <div class="p-10 bg-white rounded shadow-lg w-full">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-10 border-b">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="Company Logo" class="w-24 h-24" />
        <div class="text-right">
          <h3 class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-2xl">Invoice</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-start py-10 border-b text-black">
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-xl">Company Information</h4>
          <p>Sender Name</p>
          <p>Sender Street</p>
          <p>Sender City, Sender State, Sender Zip</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-xl">Receiver</h4>
          <p>Receiver Name</p>
          <p>Receiver Street</p>
          <p>Receiver City, Receiver State, Receiver Zip</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-xl">Receiver</h4>
          <p>Receiver Name</p>
          <p>Receiver Street</p>
          <p>Receiver City, Receiver State, Receiver Zip</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="invoice-body">
    <table class="w-full border-collapse text-black">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th class="p-2 border text-left">Service</th>
                <th class="p-2 border text-left">Description</th>
                <th class="p-2 border text-left">Rate</th>
                <th class="p-2 border text-left">QTY</th>
                <th class="p-2 border text-left">Amount</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border">Service 1</td>
                <td class="p-2 border">Description of Service 1</td>
                <td class="p-2 border">Rate of Service 1</td>
                <td class="p-2 border">Quantity of Service 1</td>
                <td class="p-2 border">Amount for Service 1</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="text-right mt-4 text-black">
        <p>Subtotal: $Subtotal</p>
        <p>VAT 10%: $VAT</p>
        <p>Total: $Total</p>
        <p>Paid To Date: $PaidToDate</p>
        <p>Balance Due: $BalanceDue</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="mt-10">
    <p>Thank you for choosing Novotech! If you have any questions or comments regarding our services, feel free to contact us.</p>
    <p>Terms: Payment is required 10 days after service has been completed. A late fee of Â£10 per day will be added to the invoice once the initial 10 days have passed and no invoice will be sent out.</p>
</div>
    </div>
    </div>
